org.spongepowered.api.world.schematic

Interface Palette<T extends CatalogType>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type this palette will maintain
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlockPalette

    public interface Palette<T extends CatalogType>
    Represents a mapping for types to a local identifier. Can be used for mapping CatalogTypes to int id's for storage purposes, or for converting stored information to a representable format back into CatalogTypes.

        int getOrAssign(T type)
        Gets the identifier for the given type T from the mapping. If the type T is not yet registered in the mapping then it is registered and given the next available identifier.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        The identifier

      • remove

        Removes the given type T from the mapping.

        Note that if this palette is considered a global palette, removal is not supported.
